The Doorbell Sessions with @jennykarrsinger strikes again!  This time we decided to feature one of my favs @kayastewart!  Kaya is the daughter of the legendary @davestewarteurythmics of rock band royalty, @eurythmicsmusic!  Over the years that I’ve had the pleasure of working with him I’ve come to know her and her incredible artistry.  She’s the coolest girl with a gravelly, gorgeous instrument for a voice and she has a new project out called “Things Go South” on all streaming platforms, so grab it! But first here is a little spontaneous cover of the now classic song, “Landslide” by our Queen Goddess, @stevienicks who is my hero and former boss lady and Kaya’s and Dave’s family friend!  What’s better than a bunch of friends sitting on a rooftop covering “Landslide!” in 3 part harmony?? Not much so here goes….

#thedoorbellsessions #landslide #harmony
